        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your regular exposure to the insidious putrescence of undeath inured you to its effects. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to saving throws made against spells and effects with the death, disease, and evil traits. Whenever you become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained] or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened], reduce the status penalty you take from the condition by 1, to a minimum of 0.</p>"
